VALUES ('ICC:CBC_Chapter11A_11B:2025:CA:11B-232.2.1.3', '11B-232.2.1.3', 'Substitute cells', 'When alterations are made to specific cells, detention and correctional facility operators may satisfy their obligation to provide the required number of cells with mobility features by providing the required mobility features in substitute cells (cells other than those where alterations are originally planned), provided that each substitute cell meets the following conditions:

