VALUES ('ICC:CBC_Chapter11A_11B:2025:CA:11B-604.8.2', '11B-604.8.2', 'Ambulatory accessible compartments.', 'Ambulatory accessible compartments shall comply with Section 11B-604.8.2.

11B-604.8.2—AMBULATORY ACCESSIBLE TOILET COMPARTMENT

Ambulatory accessible compartments shall have a depth of 60 inches (1524 mm) minimum and a width of 35 inches (889 mm) minimum and 37 inches (940 mm) maximum.

