Exception: Where toe clearance complying with Section 11B-605.5.4 is provided, the required maneuveringspace in front of the urinal fixture shall be permitted tobe reduced to 60 inches (1524 mm) minimum wide and60 inches (1524 mm) minimum deep.', 'ICC+CBC_Chapter11A_11B+2025+CA', 'accessibility', 'ICC:CBC_Chapter11A_11B:2025:CA:11B-605', 'https://codes.iccsafe.org/content/CABC2025P1/chapter-11b-accessibility-to-public-buildings-public-accommodations-commercial-buildings-and-public-housing#CABC2025P1_Ch11B_SubCh06_Sec11B_605', 'subsection', '933840337c1deeb063f0bdecac11ab677fae8fc07cce38fa59c8260181763f1c')
