VALUES ('ICC:CBC_Chapter11A_11B:2025:CA:11B-233.3.2', '11B-233.3.2', 'Residential dwelling units for sale', 'Residential dwelling units designed and constructed or altered by public entities that will be offered for sale to individuals shall provide accessible features to the extent required by this chapter.

