VALUES ('ICC:CBC_Chapter11A_11B:2025:CA:11B-809.9.1', '11B-809.9.1', 'Clear floor space.', 'Clear floor spaces 30 inches (762 mm) by 48 inches (1219 mm), with centerlines aligned with the centerline of the work surface, appliance, sink or fixture, shall be provided in the following locations:

