VALUES ('ICC:CBC_Chapter11A_11B:2025:CA:11B-703.1.1', '11B-703.1.1', 'Plan review and inspection.', 'Signs as specified in Section 11B-703, or in other sections of this code, when included in the construction of new buildings or facilities, or when included, altered or replaced due to additions, alterations or renovations to existing buildings or facilities, and when a permit is required, shall comply with Sections 11B-703.1.1.1 and 11B-703.1.1.2.

