VALUES ('ICC:CBC_Chapter11A_11B:2025:CA:11B-707.5.2', '11B-707.5.2', 'Receipts.', 'Where receipts are provided, speech output devices shall provide audible balance inquiry information, error messages and all other information on the printed receipt necessary to complete or verify the transaction.

