VALUES ('ICC:CBC_Chapter11A_11B:2025:CA:11B-1003.3.1', '11B-1003.3.1', 'Boat slip clearance.', 'Boat slips shall provide clear pier space 60 inches (1524 mm) wide minimum and at least as long as the boat slips. Each 10 feet (3048 mm) maximum of linear pier edge serving boat slips shall contain at least one continuous clear opening 60 inches (1524 mm) wide minimum.

Exceptions:

